reactor.fn.tuple

Class Tuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • reactor.fn.tuple.Tuple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Tuple1

    public class Tuple
extends Object
implements Iterable, Serializable
    A Tuple is an immutable Collection of objects, each of which can be of an arbitrary type.
    Author:
    Jon Brisbin, Stephane Maldini
